Source: lal
Section: non-free/libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Kipp Cannon <kipp@gravity.phys.uwm.edu>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), autotools-dev, libframe-dev, libmetaio-dev, libgsl0-dev, fftw3-dev
Standards-Version: 3.6.0

Package: lal
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libframe0, libmetaio0, libgsl0, fftw3
Description: LSC Algorithm Library
 LAL contains core routines for gravitational wave data analysis as used by the
 LIGO Scientific Collaboration (LSC).
 .
 This package contains the shared-object library needed to run LAL
 applications.

Package: lal-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, lal (= ${Source-Version}), libframe-dev, libmetaio-dev, libgsl0-dev, fftw3-dev
Description: LSC Algorithm Library
 LAL contains core routines for gravitational wave data analysis as used by the  LIGO Scientific Collaboration (LSC).
 .
 This package contains the files needed for building LAL programs, as
 well as the documentation for the library.
